</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/VgwkO4nWsRk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/31/chinese-researchers-achieve-quantum-advantage-in-two-mainstream-routes/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=chinese-researchers-achieve-quantum-advantage-in-two-mainstream-routes</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Photoshop 滑鼠一按選取相中物件   Sensei AI 新功能有驚喜</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/yq5tRGftg9A/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 31 Oct 2021 06:42:09 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Adobe]]></category><category><![CDATA[photoshop]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1068300</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>過去 Photoshop 給予新手用家的印象是專業，更準確地說是可能是難用。Adobe 最近發表了 Photos [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>過去 Photoshop 給予新手用家的印象是專業，更準確地說是可能是難用。Adobe 最近發表了 Photoshop 的桌面版和 iPad 更新，物件選取工具 (Object Selection Tool) 功能有所提升，更推出多款濾鏡，供用家選擇。</p><p>Adobe 於今年的 Adobe MAX 創新大會上發表 Photoshop 桌面及 iPad 版本更新。當中 Sensei AI  的更新最為驚喜，更新後，用家在物件選取工具時，直接使用滑鼠點擊，直接選取想要的圖像。有別於過往，在大多數情況下都不能精準地選取想要的物件，導致需手動選取，都頗費時。Adobe 亦指出，未來將有更多功能會隨著 Sensei AI 學習模型升級而偵測到更多物件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068301 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/27e914b0-370a-11ec-a7fd-d6de87842e12-694x397.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/27e914b0-370a-11ec-a7fd-d6de87842e12-694x397.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/27e914b0-370a-11ec-a7fd-d6de87842e12-1280x732.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/27e914b0-370a-11ec-a7fd-d6de87842e12-768x439.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/27e914b0-370a-11ec-a7fd-d6de87842e12-1536x878.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/27e914b0-370a-11ec-a7fd-d6de87842e12.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可直接使用滑鼠點擊，選取物件</p><p>另一個以 Sensei AI 推動的新功能是「為所有物件加上遮罩」，是把能辨別的物件都選取一次。</p><p>在濾鏡方面，Adobe 推出 beta 版風景混合器（Landscape Mixer）、色彩轉移（Color Transfer）和調和（Harmonization） 等 AI 濾鏡。風景混合器方面，可將兩幅風景影像結合，創造全新影像，用家甚至可創作出天馬行空，如幻象般的影像。色彩轉移則可選取特定配色，創作出不同顏色的外觀。而調和功能則將兩個圖層某個元素的顏色與另一圖層配搭。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068302 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_11af7d54452ef90d72bfec8b860c4cecacea50efc-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_11af7d54452ef90d72bfec8b860c4cecacea50efc-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_11af7d54452ef90d72bfec8b860c4cecacea50efc-1280x852.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_11af7d54452ef90d72bfec8b860c4cecacea50efc-768x511.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_11af7d54452ef90d72bfec8b860c4cecacea50efc-1536x1022.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_11af7d54452ef90d72bfec8b860c4cecacea50efc.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲風景混合器（Landscape Mixer）</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068303 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_1c92d42a8242d4312b8b80083320b6a55e7a6575a-694x268.png" alt="" width="694" height="268" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_1c92d42a8242d4312b8b80083320b6a55e7a6575a-694x268.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_1c92d42a8242d4312b8b80083320b6a55e7a6575a-1280x493.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_1c92d42a8242d4312b8b80083320b6a55e7a6575a-768x296.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_1c92d42a8242d4312b8b80083320b6a55e7a6575a-1536x592.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_1c92d42a8242d4312b8b80083320b6a55e7a6575a.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲色彩轉移（Color Transfer）</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068304 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_17278c86c8cb67c27aaf2055cd2ec5155d692772e-694x393.png" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_17278c86c8cb67c27aaf2055cd2ec5155d692772e-694x393.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_17278c86c8cb67c27aaf2055cd2ec5155d692772e-768x435.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/media_17278c86c8cb67c27aaf2055cd2ec5155d692772e.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲調和（Harmonization）</p><p>其他 AI 濾鏡亦有更新，如 Depth Blur、Superzoom、Style Transfer 和 Colorize。漸層、色彩管理及 HDR 能力也有改善。值得一提的是 Adobe 加強了 Photoshop 與 Illustrator 之間協調，Illustrator 的向量物件可被複製到 Photoshop ，並保持 Photoshop 編輯其屬性的能力。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://blog.adobe.com/en/publish/2021/10/26/photoshop-ships-major-updates-across-desktop-ipad-apps-extends-light-editing-collaboration-features-web-beta.html#gs.et0860">Adobe</a></p><p>&#8212;</p>
