</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/yq5tRGftg9A" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/31/adobe-photoshop/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=adobe-photoshop</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>日本可摺疊電動電單車，可收起放於辦工桌下</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/gXlw3cCK2C0/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 31 Oct 2021 06:41:29 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[ICOMA]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tatamel Bike]]></category><category><![CDATA[可摺疊式電動電單車]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1068353</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>不少人鍾情於電單車，原因都是因為其細小及方便性，易於在繁忙的都市裏穿梭，輕鬆駛過塞車地段。為配合其方便的特性， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>不少人鍾情於電單車，原因都是因為其細小及方便性，易於在繁忙的都市裏穿梭，輕鬆駛過塞車地段。為配合其方便的特性，日本車廠 ICOMA 宣布研發可摺疊式電動電單車「Tatamel Bike」，吸引用家購買。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068360 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1f8c277c19938b3fc77414becd85e744-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1f8c277c19938b3fc77414becd85e744-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1f8c277c19938b3fc77414becd85e744-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1f8c277c19938b3fc77414becd85e744.jpeg 824w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「Tatamel Bike」可摺疊式電動電單車</p><p>ICOMA 日前推出宣傳片，公布研發可摺疊式電動電單車「Tatamel Bike」。完全展開後尺寸達長 1230mm、高 1000mm、寬 650mm，摺疊時則為長 700mm、高 680mm、寬 260mm。「Tatamel Bike」上設有類似行李手提的把手，方便用家拖行。座墊、車頭、車燈、踏板等配置均藏在細小的車身中。「Tatamel Bike」的最大特色是用家可隨自己喜好更換車身側板，或方便公司落廣告。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068361 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/640-694x363.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/640-694x363.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/640-768x402.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/640.jpeg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可隨自己喜好更換車身側板</p><p>官方亦指，「Tatamel Bike」摺疊後，可以直接拿到公司，放在辦工桌下。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068362 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/48471e9283f1120fe0fa3575e08b76f8-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/48471e9283f1120fe0fa3575e08b76f8-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/48471e9283f1120fe0fa3575e08b76f8-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/48471e9283f1120fe0fa3575e08b76f8.jpeg 797w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「Tatamel Bike」摺疊後可放於辦工桌下</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1068363 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/a3d33ac117a71851c18af8250ede8a3d-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/a3d33ac117a71851c18af8250ede8a3d-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/a3d33ac117a71851c18af8250ede8a3d-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/a3d33ac117a71851c18af8250ede8a3d.jpeg 795w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「Tatamel Bike」摺疊後可放於辦工桌下</p><p>用家最關心的可能是動力及充電能力，「Tatamel Bike」動力是靠酸鐵鋰電池提供，極速為 40km/h，續航力達 50 公里。ICOMA 表示希望能量產「Tatamel Bike」盡快推出市面，而發佈日期與售價有待公布。</p><p>這不是第一次出現可摺疊式電單車，早在 80 年代本田車廠（Honda）推出 Motocompo 可摺疊電單車。其獨特的設計讓把手及座墊可收納在車身內，摺疊後就可以亦可輕易收藏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1068364 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/d5055641.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="383" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲本田車廠於 80 年代出產的 Motocompo</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YW-pbhwxyoc&amp;t=4s">ICOMA</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><div id="entry-content-1068188" class="entry-content" data-swiftype-name="body" data-swiftype-type="text"><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p><div class="at-below-post addthis_tool" data-url="https://unwire.hk/2021/10/28/samsung-licensing-tizen-os/wireless-home/audio-visual/"></div></div></p><div class="feedflare">
